msgid "Group two exercises into a superset so they alternate automatically during a session, ideal for pairing antagonist muscles or staying efficient between sets. Tap the three-dot menu on any exercise in the workout editor and choose Create Superset, then select the second exercise. A coloured label identifies which superset each exercise belongs to throughout the app. When you complete a set on one exercise, the app moves you straight to its superset partner."
